These are Puzzles for 3x7 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-1::.
The people perfer 7 different movie-genres: comedy, disaster, fantasy, horror, satire, scientific, superhero
House: townhouse, colonial, craftsman, victorian, art-deco, farmhouse, cottage
The people have 7 different hobbies: baking, woodworking, card-games, collecting, chess, photography, reading
 1. the person watching satire movies is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is between the colonial house and the townhouse house##2
 4. the person watching horror movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 5. the colonial house is on the left of the person watching disaster movies##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is the person who's hobby is reading##1
 7. the victorian house is between the person who's hobby is collecting and the person watching satire movies##2
 8. the person who's hobby is chess is on the left of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who's hobby is photography is on the left of the person who's hobby is baking##1
10. the person watching superhero movies is the craftsman house##1
11. the farmhouse house is the person watching horror movies##1
12. the person watching superhero movies is on the left of the person watching fantasy movies##1
13. the person who's hobby is baking is the art-deco house##1
14. the person watching scientific movies is between the person who's hobby is card-games and the person who's hobby is reading##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |     2      |     3      |    4     |   5    |     6      |    7     |
| Movie-Genre   | satire | comedy     | scientific | disaster | horror | superhero  | fantasy  |
| House   | townhouse  | victorian        | colonial  | cottage     | farmhouse   | craftsman       | art-deco   |
| Hobby         | woodworking   | reading | collecting    | card-games  | chess | photography | baking |

