 2. the person who's sport is sailing is the person who's sport is sailing##1
 3. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the fan of electronic##1
 5. the person who's sport is badminton is the person who growsaconite##1
 6. the person who growsballoon-flower is the fan of folk##1
 7. the person who growsballoon-flower is between the person who's sport is soccer and the fan of d&b##2
 8. the person who's sport is handball is on the left of the person who growszinnia##1
 9. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who's sport is parkour##1
10. the person who growsorchid is on the right of the fan of blues##1
11. the person who growszinnia is on the right of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
12. the fan of electronic is the person who growstulip##1
13. the person who growsdaffodil is on the left of the person who growsballoon-flower##1
14. the person who growsdaffodil is on the right of the fan of techno##1
15. the person who growstulip is on the far right##1
16. the person who's sport is cricket is on the left of the person who growsaconite##1

.:: Answer ::.
