.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-3::.
7 different games are played: mah-jongg, bridge, snooker, billiard, monopoly, scrabble, canasta
The people's birthday is in 7 different months: august, december, february, march, april, may, october
The people use 7 different means of transport: helicopter, roller, scooter, snowmobile, taxi, trike, van
 1. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in august##1
 2. the person driving the taxi is the person who's birthday is in march##1
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 4. the person driving the scooter is the person playing bridge##1
 5. the person driving the trike is between the person driving the van and the person who's birthday is in october##2
 6. the person driving the taxi is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the person playing scrabble##1
 8. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 9. the person driving the van is on the far right##1
10. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in may##1
11. the person driving the roller is the person who's birthday is in august##1
12. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
13. the person playing mah-jongg is on the left of the person who's birthday is in march##1
14. the person driving the van is the person playing canasta##1
15. the person driving the helicopter is on the left of the person playing monopoly##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |      5       |    6     |    7     |
| Game    | mah-jongg     | monopoly   | scrabble        | bridge   | snooker     | billiard     | canasta    |
