.:: Puzzle 3x7-Level-2-16::.
The people have 7 different jobs:  coach, dancer, fisherman, manager, musician, photographer, writer
The people use 7 different means of transport: snowmobile, taxi, trike, motorbike, airplane, tram, quad-bike
There are 7 different favourite colors: light-blue, lilac, fuchsia, chestnut, green, purple, lavender
 1. the person who likes purple is on the left of the fisherman##1
 2. the person who likes purple is between the person driving the airplane and the person driving the trike##2
 3. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who likes lilac##1
 4. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the photographer##1
 5. the person driving the snowmobile is the coach##1
 6. the fisherman is in the middle##1
 7. the musician is the person driving the tram##1
 8. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person who likes lavender##1
 9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person who likes lilac##1
10. the writer is the person who likes green##1
11. the coach is on the right of the manager##1
12. the person driving the quad-bike is on the left of the photographer##1
13. the person who likes light-blue is on the left of the person who likes fuchsia##1
14. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the coach##1
15. the writer is on the right of the person driving the airplane##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |      2       |    3     |     4      |    5     |    6    |     7      |
| Job           | dancer | photographer | musician | fisherman  | writer   | manager | coach      |
| Transport   | quad-bike | trike        | tram    | airplane     | motorbike     | taxi   | snowmobile        |
| Color           | light-blue   | fuchsia       | purple    | chestnut | green | lavender   | lilac |

