The people have 7 different hobbies: dancing, filmmaking, gardening, photography, skydiving, traveling, writing
7 different games are played: backgammon, snooker, monopoly, canasta, domino, whist, chess
 1. the old-henry-smoker is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 2. the person playing whist is in the middle##1
 3. the bolivar-smoker is on the right of the person playing domino##1
 4. the dannemann-smoker is the person who's hobby is dancing##1
 5. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing whist is the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the person playing monopoly is the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 8. the person playing canasta is between the person who's hobby is gardening and the person playing monopoly##2
 9. the person playing chess is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is in the middle##1
11. the oliveros-smoker is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the right of the person who's hobby is skydiving##1
13. the person playing canasta is on the left of the havana-smoker##1
14. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is between the person playing chess and the person who's hobby is writing##2
15. the person playing chess is the dannemann-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |    1    |     2      |    3    |      4      |     5      |      6      |     7     |
